<font color="#FF0000">SUNDAYS AND GUNBUNNYS</font><br>
<tt>Sat May 10 22:00:38 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
O.K., O.K.,  Maybe it is Mother's Day and all the other Sunday's back to back.  Could be.  When I get back from the Wall, like Art, I will share the impressions and feelings.  Many can't go, so maybe between Art and the rest of us who can go, maybe we can impart a sense of having been there.<br>
  <br>
And by the way,sir, Those were 8-inch guns,dude! That did make us the biggest and baddest in the Ia Drang in Nov. of 65.  So it ain't how far one can reach, but the impact one makes upon one's arrival. (GRIN) So this bunny(gun) one ea. type.  U.S.Army issue. sure put 260lb. things where they needed to be. 
